snippet.title: Trailer Pokémon MMO 3D - Unreal
snippet.description:
Pokémon MMO 3D has changed its game engine.
Before we used Unity3D, now it's Unreal Engine.
All the game was remade, there are big changes in graphics and battle mechanics.

Download link: https://www.indiedb.com/games/pokemon-mmo-3d-online/downloads/pokemon-mmo-3d-windows-unreal-version

Video made by MegaPixel

#pokemon #unrealengine #ue4
